21
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:04,950
♪A smile of hers
can make the whole street bloom♪

22
00:01:05,270 --> 00:01:09,020
♪How could the world ever let down
a pair like us, unmatched in the world?♪

23
00:01:09,280 --> 00:01:11,700
